{"tid":553952,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"介意男朋友住既地方細，有錯咩？","createTime":"2018-02-08T04:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T17:53:53.000Z","uid":82845,"like":5,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e67930c5a923ee66b487072369f505ea03e47d","tid":553952,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T04:37:17.000Z","msg":"我唔介意男朋友住公屋或者租屋住，我男朋友仲要係私樓添，我一心以為可以同佢係呢間屋企成家立室，點知上到去呆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來佢話俾四幾百萬買既樓，居然得三百幾呎，我屋企個客廳都唔止啦，佢話細細地咁樣幾溫馨，幾舒服，我心諗佢屋企連個浴缸都擺唔起，同我講舒服? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去完佢屋企之後我同佢講左呢個問題，話介意佢屋企咁細，佢過左幾個鍾先覆我，竟然話:「 我睇錯你，仲以為你同普通女仔唔同，但原來你同大部份香港既女仔一樣都係貪慕虛榮」，我真係唔明，介意佢地方細都有錯？仲點同你講將來？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n轉貼"},{"pid":"541c83aae0135d7380441de2492fdc976ba85433","tid":553952,"uid":102096,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T04:42:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0cd915212cf9bf29011f37738c3ae8ef3f9af60","tid":553952,"uid":9726,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4896fc9a86e385274e681551f6de911c417399e7","tid":553952,"uid":126046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"層樓 係咪佢既先？<br />\n咁層樓 你有冇出過錢？"},{"pid":"a9919c5bb635f89257e2403d387c49884610aaeb","tid":553952,"uid":139228,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"拿，做雞住套房都係100零呎連套廁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁你又係一隻<span style=\"color: red;\">雞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n住300呎已經算好撚大啦wo<br />\n<br />\n係一樓一已經算係<span style=\"color: red;\">雞后</span>先會住<br />\n<br />\n仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324eaefd431f190873abba2647e0c3011bf2f5ae","tid":553952,"uid":84102,"like":1,"di